<InfoScreen>:
    FloatLayout:
        canvas:
            Rectangle:
                size: (max(self.size)*1.5,max(self.size))
                pos: (self.pos[0] - min(self.size)*.4, self.pos[1])
                source: "image/im.jpg"
        GridLayout:
            rows:1
            pos_hint: {"top": .95, "right": 1}
            size_hint: 1, .2
            Image:
                source: "image/investigame.png"
        ScrollView:
            do_scroll_x: False
            do_scroll_y: True
            pos_hint: {"top": .75, "center_x": .5}
            size_hint: .8, .5 #width and height
            scroll_y: 1
            Label:
                size_hint_y: None
                size: self.texture_size
                text_size: self.width, None
                font_name: 'font/Montserrat.ttf'
                font_size: "14dp"
                text:
                    "Investors, resellers, and gaming enthusiasts are always interested in knowing if a new video game will be commercially successful.\nThis information can be used in a variety of ways but most importantly as a signal for investment decisions since the gaming market is very volatile.\nInvestiGame uses Machine Learning tools to calculate and predict how video games will perform on the market using social media text analytics, publisher/developer info, and professional reviews for the game.\nNew games that are about to be released are searched for and added each day to the database."
        GridLayout:
            rows:1
            pos_hint: {"top": .15, "center_x": .5}
            size_hint: .5, .1
            Button:
                background_normal: ''
                background_color: 10/255, 50/255, 80/255, .9
                text: "Game Page"
                on_release:
                    app.change_screen('game_screen')